    <p style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</p>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">The winnings are calculated by multiplying a stake by the odds. It's not possible to combine (parlay) LIVE GAMES bets. &nbsp;</p>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">Each draw has a unique number and outcomes can be found on the &ldquo;<strong>Results</strong>&rdquo; page.</p>
